{"primaryContentSections":[{"content":[{"text":"Overview","type":"heading","anchor":"Overview","level":2},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"You must implement ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"UIApplicationDelegate.application(_:continue:restorationHandler:)"},{"text":" to handle your universal links. By default, the Appcues iOS SDK will call this method for every ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"https"},{"type":"text","text":" link it tries to open to allow your app a chance to handle it internally instead of opening the link in a browser. Optionally, you may provide an allow list of URL hosts—refer to the Domain Allow List section below."}]},{"name":"Note","type":"aside","content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"If your app has opted into ","type":"text"},{"type":"reference","identifier":"https:\/\/developer.apple.com\/documentation\/uikit\/app_and_environment\/scenes","isActive":true},{"text":", you still must implement the ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"UIApplicationDelegate"},{"type":"text","text":" method to handle universal links triggered from the Appcues iOS SDK."}]}],"style":"note"},{"text":"Implementing the NSUserActivity Handler","type":"heading","anchor":"Implementing-the-NSUserActivity-Handler","level":2},{"inlineContent":[{"text":"Your implementation of ","type":"text"},{"code":"UIApplicationDelegate.application(_:continue:restorationHandler:)","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":" must return ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"true"},{"type":"text","text":" if you’ve successfully handled the link and "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"false"},{"type":"text","text":" otherwise."}],"type":"paragraph"},{"inlineContent":[{"text":"If needed, you can identify links coming from the Appcues iOS SDK by a ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"referrer"},{"text":" property in the ","type":"text"},{"code":"NSUserActivity.userInfo","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":" dictionary.","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"code":["\/\/ AppDelegate.swift","","func application(_ application: UIApplication,","                 continue userActivity: NSUserActivity,","                 restorationHandler: @escaping ([UIUserActivityRestoring]?) -> Void) -> Bool","{","","    \/\/ Get URL components from the incoming user activity.","    guard userActivity.activityType == NSUserActivityTypeBrowsingWeb,","        let incomingURL = userActivity.webpageURL else {","        return false","    }","","    if userActivity.userInfo?[\"referrer\"] as? String == \"Appcues\" {","        \/\/ This userActivity was trigged from the Appcues iOS SDK.","    }","","    \/\/ TODO: Parse the `incomingURL` here and return true if the link has been handled, false otherwise.","}"],"syntax":"swift","type":"codeListing"},{"level":2,"type":"heading","text":"Implementing a Domain Allow List","anchor":"Implementing-a-Domain-Allow-List"},{"inlineContent":[{"text":"You may define a custom key, ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"AppcuesUniversalLinkHostAllowList"},{"text":", in your ","type":"text"},{"type":"emphasis","inlineContent":[{"text":"Info.plist","type":"text"}]},{"type":"text","text":" file with an array of (string) host values to control which URLs are passed to "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"UIApplicationDelegate.application(_:continue:restorationHandler:)"},{"type":"text","text":". A URL whose host matches any of the provided host values will be treated as a potential universal link."}],"type":"paragraph"},{"inlineContent":[{"text":"An empty array will prevent all links from be treated as universal links and is functionally the same as calling ","type":"text"},{"isActive":true,"type":"reference","identifier":"doc:\/\/com.appcues.sdk\/documentation\/AppcuesKit\/Appcues\/Config\/enableUniversalLinks(_:)"},{"text":" with a ","type":"text"},{"code":"false","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":" argument."}],"type":"paragraph"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"If the "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"AppcuesUniversalLinkHostAllowList"},{"text":" key is absent from ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"Info.plist"},{"type":"text","text":", all "},{"code":"https","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":" links will be treated as potential universal links."}],"type":"paragraph"},{"inlineContent":[{"text":"Example ","type":"text"},{"type":"emphasis","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Info.plist"}]},{"text":" to only treat links to ","type":"text"},{"code":"appcues.com","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":" as universal links:","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"syntax":"plist","code":["<?xml version=\"1.0\" encoding=\"UTF-8\"?>","<!DOCTYPE plist PUBLIC \"-\/\/Apple\/\/DTD PLIST 1.0\/\/EN\" \"http:\/\/www.apple.com\/DTDs\/PropertyList-1.0.dtd\">","<plist version=\"1.0\">","<dict>","    ...","    <key>AppcuesUniversalLinkHostAllowList<\/key>","    <array>","        <string>appcues.com<\/string>","    <\/array>","<\/dict>","<\/plist>"],"type":"codeListing"}],"kind":"content"}],"metadata":{"role":"article","modules":[{"name":"AppcuesKit"}],"roleHeading":"Article","title":"Configuring Handling of Universal Links"},"identifier":{"url":"doc:\/\/com.appcues.sdk\/documentation\/AppcuesKit\/UniversalLinking","interfaceLanguage":"swift"},"kind":"article","abstract":[{"text":"The Appcues iOS SDK supports universal links as an option for deep linking to screens within your app.","type":"text"}],"seeAlsoSections":[{"title":"Navigation","generated":true,"identifiers":["doc:\/\/com.appcues.sdk\/documentation\/AppcuesKit\/Navigation","doc:\/\/com.appcues.sdk\/documentation\/AppcuesKit\/AppcuesNavigationDelegate"]}],"hierarchy":{"paths":[["doc:\/\/com.appcues.sdk\/documentation\/AppcuesKit"]]},"sections":[],"schemaVersion":{"patch":0,"major":0,"minor":3},"variants":[{"paths":["\/documentation\/appcueskit\/universallinking"],"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"swift"}]}],"references":{"doc://com.appcues.sdk/documentation/AppcuesKit/Appcues/Config/enableUniv